Operator ChannelFilter


A ChannelFilter is an Operator which selectively blocks/passes MIDI
messages based on channel.  Any number of channels may be selected
simultaneously.  Separately non-channel messages my be blocked.


Sub-Commands:

Command     op name, enable-system-events, bool
OSC         /pig/op name, enable-system-events, bool

Enables/disables filtering of MIDI system messages for named ChannelFilter

OSC Return: AKC

-----------------------------------------------------

Command     op name, q-system-events-enabled
OSC         /pig/op name, q-system-events-enabled

OSC Return: AKC bool false if MIDI system messages are filtered.

